name: OpenHandsNetwork
description: OpenHandsNetwork is fair launched DeFi Token. Three simple processes occur during each trade: Reflections: 2% of every transaction is taken and redistributed automatically to all $OHN Token holders. Liquidity Pool: 2% of every transaction contributes toward automatically generating further liquidity on PancakeSwap benefiting long term $OHN holders the most. $BNB Rewards: 2% of every transaction is taken and redistributed to all $OHN holders in $BNB. Accumulate $BNB by holding $OHN Token in your wallet!
